# Week 3

## Omnicalc

### Setup

- Make sure students are running `rails s` in their app folder, not the app's parent folder
- Make sure students test output variables after hitting submit, since the forms wont show any work from the controller

### Word count

- Make sure students are replacing `\r` with an empty string and `\n` with a space
- Make sure students aren't removing punctuation before they count characters, with our without spaces

### Loan Payment

- Make sure students are using the number of months, not years
